.TH PO-TRANSLATE 1 "February 2026" "po-translate 1.3.1" "User Commands"
.SH NÉV
po-translate \- batch translate PO and TS localization files
.SH ÁTTEKINTÉS
.B po-translate
\fB\-\-source\fR \fILANG\fR [\fB\-\-target\fR \fILANG\fR] [\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fIPATH\fR...
.SH LEÍRÁS
.B po-translate
automatically translates gettext .po and Qt .ts files using various
translation services, both free and commercial.
.PP
If \fB\-\-target\fR is not specified, the target language is detected
from the \fBLANG\fR environment variable.
.SH BEÁLLÍTÁSOK
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-source " " \fILANG\fR
Source language code (required). Example: en
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-target " " \fILANG\fR
Target language code. Defaults to system LANG.
.TP
.BR \-\-service " " \fISERVICE\fR
Translation service (default: lingva).
Available: lingva, mymemory, libretranslate, deepl, deepl-free, google, openai, anthropic
.TP
.BR \-\-api\-key " " \fIKEY\fR
API key for paid services (DeepL, Google, OpenAI, Anthropic).
.TP
.BR \-\-model " " \fIMODEL\fR
Model for AI services. Example: gpt-4o-mini, claude-3-haiku-20240307
.TP
.BR \-\-batch\-size " " \fIN\fR
Entries per API call (default: 10).
.TP
.BR \-\-dry\-run
Preview changes without saving.
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-recursive
Do not search subdirectories.
.SH SZOLGÁLTATÁSOK
.TP
.B lingva
Free, no API key required. Uses Lingva Translate instances.
.TP
.B mymemory
Free tier available. 1000 words/day without key.
.TP
.B libretranslate
Self-hosted option available. Use \-\-url for custom instance.
.TP
.B deepl, deepl-free
High quality. Requires API key.
.TP
.B google
Google Cloud Translation. Requires API key.
.TP
.B openai
GPT models with context awareness. Requires API key.
.TP
.B anthropic
Claude models with context awareness. Requires API key.
.SH KILÉPÉSI ÁLLAPOT
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Error occurred.
.SH PÉLDÁK
.TP
Translate to system language (from LANG):
.B po-translate \-\-source en messages.po
.TP
Translate English to Swedish using free service:
.B po-translate \-s en \-t sv locale/
.TP
Use DeepL with API key:
.B po-translate \-s en \-t de \-\-service deepl \-\-api\-key KEY file.po
.TP
Dry run with OpenAI:
.B po-translate \-s en \-t fr \-\-service openai \-\-dry\-run .
.SH KÖRNYEZET
.TP
.B LANG
Used as default target language if \-\-target not specified.
.TP
.B OPENAI_API_KEY
API key for OpenAI service.
.TP
.B ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
API key for Anthropic service.
.TP
.B DEEPL_API_KEY
API key for DeepL service.
